children.text: Enough Said spoken word event series event held at Bistro 4 (4040 St. Laurent, Montreal, QC, H2W 1Y8, Canada) on February 27, 1995, hosted by Lee Gotham. Feature performances by Sonja Skarstedt and Lynn Suderman. Open mic/supporting performances by Justin McGrail, Stephen Edgar, Sandra Jeppesen, Mitsiko Miller, Jacob Landesman, and more.
